                14. Copy of Official Rules and Winner List:  For a copy of these Official Rules or winner list, send a self-addressed stamped envelope with your request to 6 Soldiers Field Park APT 505, Boston, MA 02163 or go to Sponsor’s website at https://joinjuno.com.
